#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:322
msgid "I hear voices of the enemy!  The troll was right!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=Secsupporter
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:326
msgid "You talk too much, $supporter.user_description|."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:354
msgid "That's right!  Kill them!  This hell-hole needs to be destroyed!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Wait!  We're not here to stop you, we're here to kill the evil wizard "
"Scarrion."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:362
msgid "Huh!"
msgstr "Huh!"

#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:366
msgid "Well... "
msgstr "Be'..."

#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Okay.  That's why we're here, so I guess we're allies for now.  But you're "
"still invader worms, so we'll deal with things topside."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:390
msgid "Huh, a pile of trash...  Looks like it has been here for a long time."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:406
msgid ""
"These must be the remains of a king...  Huh, most of the remains crumble to "
"dust, but this armor..."
msgstr ""

#. [object]
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:412
msgid "Ancient Armor"
msgstr "Armatura ancestrale"

#. [object]
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:414
msgid ""
"This expensive looking armor is very light, but stronger than anything the "
"Ukians had ever seen..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Scarrion
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:453
msgid "The barbarians are closing in!  You know what to do General..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:457
msgid "There's the snake!  Don't let him get away!"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:463
msgid "Kill Scarrion"
msgstr "Uccidi Scarrion"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:471
msgid "Scarrion Escapes"
msgstr "Scarrion fuggeFuga della carovana"

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:509
msgid "Press on!  He can't have gone far!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Scarrion
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:529
msgid ""
"Haha!  You cannot stop me, Lorenzon.  No one can stop me!  This will be your "
"grave..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:549
msgid "Gha...  There will be others...  We'll clean out this rat's nest..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:563
msgid "Graaahhh!"
msgstr "Graaahhh!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:569
msgid "Oh no!  Did he just escape again?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:573
msgid ""
"He seemed more upset, I think we may have defeated him this time.  In any "
"case, we need to get out of here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tahn Garath
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:577
msgid ""
"We agreed not to fight each other down here.  We will honour that, but we "
"will still drive you dogs out of the northlands!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:595
msgid ""
"A book, it looks like a diary.  I shouldn't pry, but let's see what the last "
"page says..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:599
msgid ""
"These people are worse than I thought.  The things they say are true.  There "
"really are such gods and they do not look kindly upon us.  The nightmare of "
"the last few days will be over soon, even if they don't find me.  I find "
"solace in my faith and my gods are not like the ones that reign down here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:615
msgid "This skeleton clutches an amulet..."
msgstr ""

#. [object]
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:622
msgid "This amulet will make melee weapons arcane."
msgstr ""
"Questo amuleto rende esoteriche le armi per il combattimento ravvicinato."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:643
msgid "Arhg!  I've fallen to infadels?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:647
msgid "He was here to slow us down.  We must stop Scarrion!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:656
msgid "That can't be good, let's pick up the pace..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:666
msgid "Time is running out.  Move!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lorenzon
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:676
msgid "What the hell was that!?!?"
msgstr "Cosa diamine è stato?!?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Scarrion
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:680
msgid "Haha!  You're too late!  Take a good look..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Scarrion
#: Bad_Moon_Rising/scenarios/J_Pit.cfg:689
msgid "... at your grave!"
msgstr ""

